snippet.title: Paper Sky - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Here it is!
I'm thrilled to unveil my latest project: 'Paper Sky,' an exhilarating paper plane adventure! Dive into the skies, experience speed like never before!
Wishlist the game on the official Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1617230
